{"tid":2318211,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得曼聯輸波迪基亞責任好大","createTime":"2020-12-09T07:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T15:45:52.000Z","uid":367552,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4351c9b927daae93f483ad699d733a90d7437e9a","tid":2318211,"uid":367552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"屌你成撚日人哋射波一啲飛搏嘅意識都冇 同埋啲出迎決定好撚差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXfZCvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXfZCvJ.png&h=c86aff17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一球<br />\n你落地搏下都好呀大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNGVaRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNGVaRk.png&h=5fb9a57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二球<br />\n呢球以佢水平絕對可以救到 但離門太近 唔怪佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6F5iS4Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6F5iS4Z.png&h=24545780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三球<br />\n屌你老母 咁撚錫身 咪撚踢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> M5係走甩佢 但係咪可以早一步出嚟迫呢呢 <br />\n<br />\n雖然我屌迪基亞 但最大戰犯都係m5 同 l2 呢兩條冚家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵隊u10啲防守意識都好撚過你哋 同埋我都唔撚知蘇b用撚死迪基亞 癲軒呢一刻一定好撚過佢 迪基亞大賽派膠都唔係第一日嘅時 anyway Ole out!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380174f25dac88634518c09436b6f109e5d05d17","tid":2318211,"uid":84081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"Ole接手後13連勝喎<br />\n英超作客連勝紀錄又破埋<br />\n仲想點？<br />\n<br />\n#SaveOle"},{"pid":"cf09f5f0136d5e9055d0c36d2e984e0d3b2dfc07","tid":2318211,"uid":367552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"380174f25dac88634518c09436b6f109e5d05d17","tid":2318211,"uid":84081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"Ole接手後13連勝喎<br />\n英超作客連勝紀錄又破埋<br />\n仲想點？<br />\n<br />\n#SaveOle"},"cited